Architecture: any
Depends: ${ocaml:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: ${ocaml:Provides}
Description: Unicode Library
 Small Unicode library with support for UTF-8, UTF-16LE, UTF-16BE, UTF32-LE,
 and UTF32-BE. All encodings have a unified interface with only their internal
 representation being different.
 .
 This package contains the shared runtime libraries.
